-- VimpelCom’s Russia Unit Will Consider Possible Bond Buyback
-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 2012-03-13T17:10:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/vimpelcom-says-it-ll-consider-buying-back-bonds-at-board-meeting.html
The Russian unit of  VimpelCom Ltd. (VIP) ,
the country’s third-biggest mobile carrier by subscribers, will
consider a possible buyback of bonds at a board meeting
tomorrow, the company said in a regulatory filing.  The statement didn’t say whether the company intends to
repurchase foreign debt or ruble bonds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
